data.description: Over 14 acres of prime real estate in a private and secluded location adjacent to the Decker’s Creek Rail Trail in Brookhaven. The possibilities are endless with this large piece of land! Subdivide and build Morgantown’s newest development or have the backyard of your dreams with plenty of room to ride 4 wheelers, horses or whatever your heart desires! Located at the end of a dead-end street on a cul-de-sac in Eastgate Manor. No HOA. Utilities available. Contact listing agent for a property tour!
